mkdir DockerComposeFile							                → Create folder

cd DockerComposeFile							                → Open folder

notepad docker-compose.yml						                → Create compose file

---[ docker-compose.yml ]------

services:
  web:
    image: nginx
    ports:
      - "9090:80"

  database:
    image: redis

-----------------------------

docker-compose config							                → Validate compose file

docker-compose up -d							                → Start containers in background

docker-compose ps							                → Show running containers

Browse: localhost:9090							                → Open NGINX webpage
